data.description: Motivated Sellers offer HUGE PRICE IMPROVEMENT!  Move in ready on an acre! This charming country home is nestled in a beautiful landscape surrounded by mature trees and offers complete privacy and serenity. The updated kitchen features custom cabinets with matching island and breakfast bar, perfect for those mornings on the go. Enjoy the desired open floorplan with vaulted ceilings that give this home an inviting, spacious feel. Relax in one of two enclosed porches perfect for winterizing plants or just taking in the view of your lush 1.15 acres of land! With four bedrooms and a bonus room, you’ll have plenty of space for family, friends, or even a hobby room! Plus, don't miss out on the 23x33 ft shop wired for electric-- ideal for all your shop needs!  Conveniently located just an hour east of Dallas. Fall in love at first sight and make it yours!
